{
  "stem": "2723.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There, I met, at that point, when we were taken to Ravensbruck, um, someone who is still here in Australia, who was there, sitting and nursing her dying mother in her lap.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the mother eventually died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she told me that things are not as bad there anymore as they were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was taken to different barracks, to a different area of the camp that I had been to before.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Um, and at that stage, I think I was wafting through various worlds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I couldn't sustain my fantasy world anymore of princes and princesses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And it was too difficult to live that life, of all the beautiful things that were going to happen later.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I got very ill with typhoid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I remember just this uncontrollable stream of bowel action and the fear of being punished for doing just that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But it just all became impossible to control.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I could no longer exercise anything over myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And there we were, at that stage not working, but there was something far worse happening.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Um, they just didn't know what to do with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And the only way to handle us was to make us stand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we stood and stood and stood for most of the day, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] absolutely unable to maintain it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then one day, there was a great flurry in the camp that the Red Cross was coming for a visit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And it became like another bizarre situation, where we were made to stand to attention, were told to make the best of our faces, were given normal clothes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we were told if we carried off this farce of looking happy little people, we were going to get Red Cross parcels.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "It was terribly difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
